long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Monitors your actions while taking an online exam on PracBee - https://abhyas.pracbee.com/

By installing this extension, you are giving PracBee permission to track your actions during an examination.

FOR TEST TAKERS:

Once you have installed the extension, please follow: 'STEP 2 - complete the system check' in the email you have received about your exam. If you have any difficulties downloading this extension, please contact our chat support. It will be available for you during step 2. Alternatively you can contact our chat support at https://abhyas.pracbee.com.
